{"/service/ndnp/nmu/batch_nmu_dogbane_ver01/data/sn93061711/00280773712/1908032101/0856.xml":{"full_text":"-OUR GREAT\nANNUAL LIMIT SALE\ni In anticipation of this great sale our buyer spent about four weeks searching the markets of St.\nLouis, Chicago and New York for values. His efforts were fuiiy repaid and we are going to demonstrate\nto the people of Quay county the sensational purchasing power of a dollar. The recent financial panic\nleft numbers of manufacturers and jobbers in a bad way overloaded with merchandise and short on\ncash, and on this account we made some very satisfactory purchases.\nOur stock is larger, better selected and more comprehensive than ever before\nWe call thi the \"Limit Sale\" because quantities are limited and we are forced to limit each\ncustomer to certain quantities on some lines, and the time is limited in which to avail vourself of\nthese matchless values J\nOur store will be closed all day Wednesday and Thursday, March 18 and 19,\narranging and marking down for this sale\nThi will be the greatest sale ever held in Tucumcari. Extra sales people to wait on the crowds.\nHose\nLadies fast black, with white feet\n15c values; limit sale price 3 pairs\nNo. 1 120 ladies mercerized lace\nhose; a 25c value, limit sale price\nNo. 404 ladies black, Burson seam\nless; regular 25c, limit sale price\n30 dozeu ladies lace lisle hose, 50c\nto 75c sellers, limit sale price\nNo. 1 1 1 child's tan hose, fast color\na 2 for 25c value, limit sale price,\n3 pairs\nNo. 106 misses fast black ribbed\nhose, the equal of most 15c val\nues, limit sale price\nNo. 117 misses white lace, 25c\nvalues, limit dale price\nNo. po boys heavy ribbed hose,\na 20c value, limit sale price 2 prs\nMen's heavy grey socks, good\nweight and finish, limit sale price\n(Not oyer 5 pairs to one customer)\nMen's heavy grey socks, regular\n10c value, limit sale price 2 pairs\nMen's extra heavy grey socks, our\nregular 15c grade, limit sale price\nMen's sample socks, worth 150 to\n25c, limit sale price 2 pairs\n25c\n15c\n19c\n39c\n25c\n11c\n15c\n25c\n5c\n15c\n10c\n25c\nHouse Furnishings\n35c red and blue checked table\ndamask\n60-inch bleuch table damask, a\n50c value\n72-inch bleach union damask,\nvery special\n64-inch bleach mercerized damask\n75c value\n72-inch bleach mercerized damask\njSi.oo value\nSome handsome match sets iu\nhemstitched table cloths and nap\nkins to match, at per set 4.50 to\n54-inch tapestry for couch covers,\nportierres, etc., fi value, yard..\n54 inch velour tapestry, regular\n$1.50 yard, special\n29c\n29c\n69c\n59c\n75c\n$11.50\n50c\n$1.00\nLadies' Neckwear\nOnly new things; no old stork on hand.\nRegular 25c collars iSc\nRegular 35c collars 19c\nRegular 50c collars 25c\nVeilings, Malines, Etc.\n25c Net Veilings 15c\n35c Net Veilings 25c\n35c Chiffon Veilings 25c\n50c Chiffon Veilings 39c\nMalines in all popular shades, vard 20c\n42-in. Chiffons, 75c quality 59c\nLadies Belts\nWe've made just two lots of all belts in the\nhouse\nLot No. 1, worth 25c to 50c 1 u\nchoice JL7C\nLot No. 2, worth 75c to $1.50\nchoice\n49c\nRugs\nCrex grass rugs, 27x54 75c\n41 36x72 $1.19\nDexter rugs, 27x54 95c\nAxminster rugs, 27x54 $2.25\n36x72 $3.50\n9x12 Brussels and Axminster art\nsquares, specially priced, $13.75,\n$15.75, $19.00, $24.00 and $25.90\nTable oil cloth, the best 15c\nTapestry couch covers 1 1 9 to $1.90\nTapestry table covers, 2 yds sq $1.75\nCurtain Swiss 8c to 25c\n18-in. bleach Turkish toweling 12c\nSwiss curtains, milled, special $1.19\n6-feet window shades, cloth 25c\nBrass curtain rods 3 for 25c\n15- inch cotton crash 5c\n16- inch cotton crash 7 l-2c\nLadies Furnishings\nLadies white waists, a\nspecial purchase, to go at\nvery low prices, in sheer\nlawns, nets and wash silks.\nPrices range from Jc\n50c to pO\nThere's a sure saving here\nof from 25c to $1 on every\nwaist\n1 .1 I\nI\nLadies Skirts\nLadies blue and grey chain-\nbray wash skirts, trimmed\nwith white bands. Cheap\nat 75c, limit sale rrk\nprice 2UC\n100 purple skirts in both\nwool and wash materials,\nreally worth up to\n$2.50, choice\nOur line of dress skirtc\nconsists of just what every particular lady\ncould want; about 20 different styles and\nmaterials, in brown, black, navy M 1 50\nand greys. Prices $2. 50 to pll.\n(Our $5-90 voile skirt is the same others ask $to for)\n$1 07i lM-\nLong Silk and Lisle Gloves\nThese, everybody must have. Fashion de\nmands it. We can't take space to\ndescribe every kind, but safe to\nsay we have the largest stock and\nthe greatest assortment outside of\nthe city stores. We have them in\nblack, white, tans, navy, Copenha\ngen and greys. We'll guarantee\na saving of 25c to 50c on every\npair, and can fit all hands.\nAlso some special values in short gloves at\n25c and 50c","height":"29212","width":"19924"}}
